HEADWORD: parking
<hw>parking</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>The act of maneuvering a vehicle
into a location where it can be left temporarily.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A space or spaces in which a vehicle can be parked;
<as>as, there is plenty of <ex>parking</ex> behind the
store</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Parkinsonia</ent>⟦br⟧
